types.html:
baumifique (plural baumifiques)

  1. Wholesome.
  2. Promoting moral and mental well-being.
  3. Decent; innocuous; sweet.
  4. Favourable to morals, religion or prosperity; sensible; conducive to good; salutary; promoting virtue or being virtuous.
trans: Favourable to morals, religion or prosperity
